
release-XXX-XXX
  o completely revised routing algorithm for improved performance and
        convergence.
  o many stability improvements
  o support for compiling the router for MIPS
  o prototype RPC protocol and stub generator

release-8-25-2008
  o Single-phase UDP and IP interfaces
  o Elimination of buffer pool
  o Fragment forwarding without hop-by-hop reassembly
  o Improved header structure to allow easy insertion/deletion
  o Network programming support using TFTP-like protocol along with parts of deluge (will become TFTP in the future). 

release-7-15-2008
  o initial release 
